      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>新疆葵花籽产品页</title>\n<style>\n    body {\n        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n        background-color: #F4F4F5;\n        margin: 0;\n        padding: 0;\n        color: #333;\n    }\n    .container {\n        display: grid;\n        grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;\n        gap: 20px;\n        max-width: 1200px;\n        margin: auto;\n        padding: 20px;\n    }\n    section, aside, div {\n        background-color: #fff;\n        padding: 15px;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n    }\n    h1, h2, h3, h4 {\n        margin-top: 0;\n        color: #8B4513;\n    }\n    #product-showcase img {\n        width: 100%;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n    }\n    #pricing-info {\n        background-color: #FFD700;\n        color: #8B4513;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    #purchase-module button {\n        padding: 10px 20px;\n        margin: 5px;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        font-size: 16px;\n    }\n    #purchase-module button:first-child {\n        background-color: #FF4500;\n        color: #fff;\n    }\n    #purchase-module button:last-child {\n        background-color: #8B4513;\n        color: #fff;\n    }\n    #promo-banner {\n        background-color: #FF4500;\n        color: #fff;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    #promo-banner span {\n        font-weight: bold;\n        display: block;\n    }\n    #interaction-features ul {\n        list-style: none;\n        padding: 0;\n    }\n    #interaction-features li {\n        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\n        padding: 5px 0;\n    }\n    #customer-service button {\n        background-color: #FFD700;\n        color: #8B4513;\n        padding: 8px 16px;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    #recommendation-section div {\n        display: flex;\n        gap: 10px;\n    }\n    .product-card {\n        flex: 1;\n        background-color: #F4F4F5;\n        padding: 10px;\n        border-radius: 6px;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    .product-card img {\n        width: 100%;\n        border-radius: 6px;\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"container\">\n    <div>\n        <section id=\"product-showcase\">\n            <h1>优质新疆葵花籽</h1>\n            <img src=\"sunflower-seeds.jpg\" alt=\"新疆葵花籽\">\n            <p>精选自新疆产区的葵花籽，颗粒饱满，口感香脆，提供多种规格包装，适合家庭与零售需求。</p>\n        </section>\n        <section id=\"pricing-info\">\n            <h2>现价与促销</h2>\n            <p>限时优惠价仅 ¥29.9，原价 ¥39.9，让您享受高品质同时节省开支。</p>\n        </section>\n        <section id=\"purchase-module\">\n            <button>立即购买</button>\n            <button>加入购物车</button>\n        </section>\n        <div id=\"promo-banner\">\n            <span>限时优惠</span>\n            <p>库存紧张，促销期间赶快入手！</p>\n        </div>\n        <section id=\"interaction-features\">\n            <h3>用户评分</h3>\n            <ul>\n                <li>★★★★★ 很香很好吃！</li>\n                <li>★★★★☆ 颗粒饱满，回购多次。</li>\n                <li>★★★★★ 外包装很精美。</li>\n            </ul>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n        <aside id=\"customer-service\">\n            <h4>客服中心</h4>\n            <button>联系客服</button>\n        </aside>\n        <section id=\"recommendation-section\">\n            <h3>推荐产品</h3>\n            <div>\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"pumpkin-seeds.jpg\" alt=\"南瓜籽\">\n                    <p>优质南瓜籽</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"nuts-mix.jpg\" alt=\"坚果混合\">\n                    <p>健康坚果混合</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>"
